Offside;;74;;94;;PG;;Since women are banned from soccer matches, Iranian females masquerade as males so they can slip into Tehran's stadium to see the game between Iran and Bahrain. The ones who are caught and arrested are taken to a holding area and guarded by soldiers. One sympathetic soldier agrees to watch the game through a peephole and recount the action to the impatient fans.;;Comedy;;Jafar Panahi;;2006;;Sima Mobarakshai,Safar Samandar,Shayesteh Irani,Mohamad Kheirabadi,Aida Sadeghi,Golnaz Farmani,Mahnnaz Zabihi,Nazanin Sediq-zadeh;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/offside